note._content: Qué hace este mocoso entre un grupo de hombres?

note._content: Only a man sure of his position in a company could pose like this (especially in centre front row)
note.author: 20941479@N00

note._content: it could be a medical condition.. in fact, looks like he's blind.
note.author: 25588517@N06

note._content: I think this man (dressed differently) may be the "teacher" -- or otherwise "head" of this "group".
note.author: 43854658@N00

note._content: Hey everybody, lets dress up real nice and pose near this trash.
note.author: 16865477@N07

note._content: I like how they set up their office chairs in rows first, & the people on top climbed on top of the chairs.
note.author: 39667115@N06

note._content: This honcho is the leader! He is up front as every one is surrounding him and behind him. Look at his pose! It is saying I own you lot! The two guys to the right and left help him run the show by keeping a tight ship. Look at their posture, both of them are pretty much closed!
note.author: 11629263@N03

note._content: This man is someone assoicated with the group but does not work with them. He would have been is respected enough to have been invited to join the group most likely by the man in the front center.
